title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 8/8 - Vikes Bites & BMac!
description: Vikes Bites and talkers early on to start the show, followed by an appearance by former Vikings LT Bryant McKinnie! He, along with former Bears DT Tommie Harris, are promoting their work with the NFL Players Choir which will be seen performing on America's Got Talent tomorrow night.
